00:49:04,440 --> 00:49:07,967
You were in the hospital
for three months, sweetheart.

715
00:49:20,957 --> 00:49:25,155
I have to talk to this doctor.
I need to hear it from him.

716
00:49:25,461 --> 00:49:27,452
You have heard it, sweetie.
Many times.

717
00:49:29,465 --> 00:49:30,864
I have?

718
00:49:32,468 --> 00:49:34,026
I'll take her.

719
00:49:35,471 --> 00:49:38,133
I have to hear for myself too.

720
00:49:48,985 --> 00:49:51,180
Doug, just take this, okay?
I can't...

721
00:49:51,215 --> 00:49:53,649
I can't look at it anymore.

722
00:49:54,490 --> 00:49:58,119
- It's gonna be all right, Luce.
- Don't call me Luce. I barely know you.

723
00:49:58,494 --> 00:50:00,724
Sweetie, you're sort of dating him.

724
00:50:01,998 --> 00:50:04,364
Sorry I'm not better-looking.

725
00:50:06,502 --> 00:50:09,130
What else happened
since last October?

726
00:50:09,505 --> 00:50:13,305
- What about my students?
- Miss Campbell took over your class.

727
00:50:16,012 --> 00:50:18,947
- Did Alicia marry that guy?
- Yeah.

728
00:50:19,015 --> 00:50:21,381
Doug, did you win
the Mr. Hawaii contest?

729
00:50:21,517 --> 00:50:23,815
I didn't know there was gonna be
a urine test.

730
00:50:24,520 --> 00:50:25,748
Wow.

731
00:50:27,023 --> 00:50:28,388
Do we have sex?

732
00:50:30,026 --> 00:50:33,894
No, we don't.
Just so everybody knows that.

733
00:50:35,031 --> 00:50:36,259
We want to.

734
00:50:37,533 --> 00:50:39,228
Just kidding.

735
00:50:43,039 --> 00:50:46,736
So you guys have to just lie
to me every day.

736
00:51:00,556 --> 00:51:02,683
Hey, Lucy.
Good to see you again.

737
00:51:05,561 --> 00:51:07,654
What the hell's her problem?

738
00:51:08,064 --> 00:51:10,589
She doesn't remember
who you are, brah.

739
00:51:10,624 --> 00:51:12,431
Oh, yeah.

740
00:51:12,568 --> 00:51:15,332
I suck at this job.

741
00:51:17,073 --> 00:51:19,007
Lucy, these are your
brain scans here.

742
00:51:19,075 --> 00:51:21,321
I'm afraid they show
no improvement.

743
00:51:21,356 --> 00:51:23,568
The temporal lobe
was severely damaged.

744
00:51:24,080 --> 00:51:27,048
What we believe is scar tissue
here is impairing your ability...

745
00:51:27,083 --> 00:51:30,746
...to convert short-term memory into
long-term memory while you sleep.

746
00:51:31,087 --> 00:51:33,851
The condition's come to be known
as Goldfield Syndrome.

747
00:51:34,090 --> 00:51:37,287
- Who's Goldfield?
- A brilliant Lithuanian psychiatrist.

748
00:51:37,593 --> 00:51:39,560
He himself suffered
temporal-lobe damage.

749
00:51:39,595 --> 00:51:41,688
Took him four years
to publish his findings...

750
00:51:42,098 --> 00:51:44,760
...because he had to keep
starting over from scratch.

751
00:51:45,101 --> 00:51:48,468
Obviously, your sense of humor
is still intact, and that's here.

752
00:51:48,604 --> 00:51:50,367
Magnificent amygdala as well.

753
00:51:50,606 --> 00:51:53,507
- Doctor, I have a question.
- I'd be happy to answer it...

754
00:51:53,609 --> 00:51:58,012
...but as I've told you before, this is a
hygienic facility. Shirts are required.

755
00:51:58,114 --> 00:51:59,547
- Oh, okay.
- Nice move.

756
00:52:01,617 --> 00:52:03,312
Listen, doctor, this...

757
00:52:03,619 --> 00:52:07,248
