759
00:52:09,625 --> 00:52:11,650
Could there be a connection
between them?

760
00:52:11,685 --> 00:52:13,458
Douglas, get off the juice.

761
00:52:13,629 --> 00:52:16,655
As for the nocturnal emissions,
why don't you take a swim...

762
00:52:17,133 --> 00:52:21,001
...buy a shirt with no holes,
find a wahine and take her to dinner.

763
00:52:21,137 --> 00:52:23,332
I'll tell my friend you said so.

764
00:52:24,140 --> 00:52:26,870
In any case, Lucy,
your condition is stable...

765
00:52:27,143 --> 00:52:28,735
...but most likely permanent.

766
00:52:29,145 --> 00:52:31,079
I'm so sorry, dear.

767
00:52:31,147 --> 00:52:32,842
But it could be worse.

768
00:52:34,650 --> 00:52:36,015
Yeah? How?

769
00:52:36,152 --> 00:52:38,985
I think you should meet
Ten Second Tom.

770
00:52:39,071 --> 00:52:42,802
Callahan Institute is the leading
brain-injury clinic in the Pacific Rim.

771
00:52:43,159 --> 00:52:46,424
We are funded out of Sandusky, Ohio
by T.B. Callahan...

772
00:52:46,662 --> 00:52:49,927
...the automotive-components tycoon
and philanthropist.

773
00:52:54,670 --> 00:52:57,195
And now, I would like
to introduce to you...

774
00:52:57,673 --> 00:53:00,506
...our most distinguished
clinical subject...

775
00:53:00,676 --> 00:53:02,075
