776
00:53:02,178 --> 00:53:03,770
- Hi. I'm Tom.
- Henry.

777
00:53:03,805 --> 00:53:04,907
- Marlin.
- Doug.

778
00:53:05,181 --> 00:53:06,409
- Lucy.
- Hi.

779
00:53:06,682 --> 00:53:08,843
Cool flip-flops.
Where'd you get them?

780
00:53:09,185 --> 00:53:12,211
You like those? It's interesting.
I was on the North Shore...

781
00:53:12,246 --> 00:53:13,416
Hi, I'm Tom.

782
00:53:14,190 --> 00:53:16,158
- Henry.
- Hi.

783
00:53:16,192 --> 00:53:18,183
- Marlin.
- Tom lost part of his brain...

784
00:53:18,694 --> 00:53:21,390
...in a hunting accident.
His memory lasts 10 seconds.

785
00:53:21,697 --> 00:53:23,164
I was in an accident? That's terrible.

786
00:53:23,199 --> 00:53:25,326
Don't worry.
You'll get over it in seconds.

787
00:53:25,701 --> 00:53:29,159
Get over it? I mean, what happened?
Did I get shot in the brain...?

788
00:53:29,205 --> 00:53:31,435
- Hi, I'm Tom.
- Hi, I'm Lucy.

789
00:53:31,707 --> 00:53:32,969
- Hi.
- Doug.

790
00:53:33,209 --> 00:53:34,437
- Hey.
- Marlin.

791
00:53:34,710 --> 00:53:37,235
Hey, Tom, can I tell you a secret?

792
00:53:39,715 --> 00:53:42,775
Don't you think you're a little old
to still have wet dreams?

793
00:53:46,222 --> 00:53:49,055
- They liked that.
- Hi, I'm Tom.

794
00:53:49,225 --> 00:53:51,557
- Yeah, watch yourself, Tom.
- Easy.

795
00:54:05,741 --> 00:54:08,141
- I'm gonna go to sleep.
- All right. Good night.

796
00:54:08,244 --> 00:54:10,838
Good night, you guys.
I'll see you tomorrow.

797
00:54:12,748 --> 00:54:15,342
- And I guess I'll see you too?
- Oh, yeah.

798
00:54:15,751 --> 00:54:17,810
You had a rough day today.
I'm sorry.

799
00:54:17,845 --> 00:54:19,948
I hope you get some rest tonight.

800
00:54:20,756 --> 00:54:22,223
Okay.

801
00:54:22,258 --> 00:54:23,725
Good night.

802
00:54:24,260 --> 00:54:25,522
So how you getting home?

803
00:54:25,761 --> 00:54:27,854
- You gonna take the Likelike or...
- Hey.

804
00:54:30,266 --> 00:54:32,996
Thank you for being
so nice to me today.

805
00:54:33,269 --> 00:54:35,829
- Sure.
- I don't want you to...

806
00:54:35,864 --> 00:54:37,466
