845
00:56:37,393 --> 00:56:40,726
- Who's your friend, Lucy?
- Oh, well, I mean, I don't know.

846
00:56:40,896 --> 00:56:43,194
We just met, but look.

847
00:56:43,399 --> 00:56:45,230
I have a secret admirer.

848
00:56:45,401 --> 00:56:48,029
Oh, really? What's this?

849
00:56:48,404 --> 00:56:49,894
It's a videotape.

850
00:56:50,406 --> 00:56:51,873
A videotape of what?

851
00:56:51,907 --> 00:56:54,068
I have no idea.

852
00:56:54,410 --> 00:56:56,207
But I have to find out.

853
00:56:57,413 --> 00:56:58,903
Happy birthday, Daddy.

854
00:56:58,914 --> 00:57:01,940
- Thank you, sweetie.
- That's right. Happy birthday, sir.

855
00:57:01,975 --> 00:57:03,851
- What are you, 200 today?
- That's cute.

856
00:57:04,420 --> 00:57:07,446
- What are you doing?
- I wanted to try something different.

857
00:57:07,481 --> 00:57:09,857
If it doesn't work,
we've only wasted one day.

858
00:57:29,445 --> 00:57:31,208
Martha Stewart faced charges...

859
00:57:33,949 --> 00:57:35,348
Oh, God!

860
00:58:15,991 --> 00:58:17,686
Okay, I think it's on. Go. Go.

861
00:58:17,993 --> 00:58:20,154
Aloha! I'm Henry Roth.

862
00:58:20,496 --> 00:58:26,492
We met here at the Hukilau Cafe
about a year after your accident.

863
00:58:26,502 --> 00:58:29,528
I like you and you like me, most days.

864
00:58:30,005 --> 00:58:33,270
Every day is different, but basically
this is what happens, Lucy.

865
00:58:33,509 --> 00:58:34,942
Kikikoloko, take the camera.

866
00:58:35,010 --> 00:58:36,272
- I got it.
- Don't drop it.

867
00:58:36,512 --> 00:58:38,537
Okay, all right.
Here we are, right here.

868
00:58:39,014 --> 00:58:41,346
The part of you in this reenactment...

869
00:58:41,381 --> 00:58:43,678
...will be played
by my good friend, Ula.

870
00:58:44,520 --> 00:58:47,080
Aloha. Sorry about your brain.

871
00:58:48,023 --> 00:58:49,422
I had a accident too.

872
00:58:49,525 --> 00:58:52,426
Believe it or not, this my good eye.

873
00:58:53,028 --> 00:58:54,256
- We ready?
- Yeah.

874
00:58:54,530 --> 00:58:58,227
Hi. I like that waffle teepee
that you have built.

875
00:58:58,534 --> 00:59:02,436
Oh! So nice of you to notice.
