and my friend's unstable.

886
00:59:28,063 --> 00:59:30,759
Come on, stop with the licking!
You're making me sick.

887
00:59:30,794 --> 00:59:32,090
Lucy, I'm sorry.

888
00:59:32,568 --> 00:59:37,096
Anyways, I know you wish I was
