with you again?

949
01:03:24,299 --> 01:03:25,561
Yes, ma'am.

950
01:03:26,802 --> 01:03:28,030
You asshole!

951
01:03:28,303 --> 01:03:31,363
You don't even open the fricking car
door for me anymore.

952
01:03:32,307 --> 01:03:33,672
You're in trouble.

953
01:03:34,810 --> 01:03:36,437
I gotta go tinkle.

954
01:03:40,816 --> 01:03:44,308
Okay, so tell me a little bit more
about yourself.

